  "body": "The Altair fork changes the calculation of rewards and penalties in several ways, and although those have been reviewed (thanks @barnabemonnot and others), we should review the implementation to reduce rounding errors.\r\n\r\nE.g. Base rewards are calculated per increment, and only then applied, instead of factoring in the effective balance first. The result is a very tiny potential loss in rewards or penalties. See https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2374#discussion_r625823381\r\n",
